Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.92,ED-shade,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里面是紧张★紧张Party
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.88,ED,,0,0,0,,容纳我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.88,ED-shade,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}容纳我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.88,0:18:30.38,ED,,0,0,0,,自己和大家Pretty♡LoveLove
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:30.38,ED-shade,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己和大家Pretty♡LoveLove
